    public interface UiWidgetPanel<CHILD extends UiWidget>
extends UiWidgetRegularComposite<CHILD>
    This is the interface for an UiWidgetRegularComposite that represents a panel. A panel is a widget that acts as a container for other widgets organizing them in a specific layout. Such widget may also be called container or layout.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Joerg Hohwiller (hohwille at users.sourceforge.net)
